Dan in some private email) some variation of that patch will most
likely appear in 2.0.47.

But I didn't like the thought of wholesale changes to the menu code at
this point in time, which is why it's not in there now, although I do
agree that it needs to be cleaned up.  I figured that after 2.1.0
would be better, but perhaps not for this particular instance.

