was the ability to provide different attributes (fg & bg colors,
fonts, etc) for individual menu items, which has been requested in the
past, and a cleaner way to specify the pixmaps.  It thought a slight
enhancement to the menu syntax might be in order which would acomplish
both - an optional field between the string and the action, perhaps
like so:

AddToMenu RootMenu "Root Menu"  {Color red/black}        Title
